Mobile phone giants, Tecno Mobile, said it is committed to promoting healthy lifestyle to enhance productivity. In a statement at the weekend, it said in demonstration of this commitment, it has sponsored what it tagged: Thank You Concert at which award-winning musician, Victor Ad, performed. The concert, held at Auchi Polytechnic, Edo State, was well attended by students and visitors. The Wetin We Gain  hit song music star, Victor Ad, who graced the event performed many of his hit songs to the delight of the audience. “Not only did Tecno showed it is for Nigerians across the country by sponsoring this colourful, proudly Nigerian concert in Auchi,  it also showed a soft spot for its fans by setting aside a special VIP section for Tecno fans at the event plus lots of gift items for everyone in the audience,” the statement explained. 